snippet.title: Amber Heard Reacts To Facing YEARS Of Jail Time!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Reacts To Facing YEARS Of Jail Time!
Amber Heard claimed that Johnny Depp had physically and emotionally attacked her. Their first legal battle in 2015 resulted in a restraining order against Johnny Depp, but it was also at this time that the fuzzy lines began. Amber Heard's stylist confirmed Johnny's claim that Amber lied about her black eye in court.
